criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age ≥ 18 years;

          -  Cancer of the upper aerodigestive tract (oral cavity, oropharynx, larynx, hypopharynx,
             rhinopharynx, salivary glands, facial sinuses, orbital cavity, ear);

          -  Cancer confirmed by histopathological analysis;

          -  Therapeutic protocol including radiotherapy.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  History of head and neck cancer;

          -  History of head and neck irradiation;

          -  Synchronous head and neck cancer.
